{"sections":[{"kind":"hero","title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","image":"ic_unified_ds.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Discovering a new framework can be exciting and scary. Learn how you can embed and use OUDS Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"With this tutorial you will learn fundamental concepts of Orange Unified Design System and discover the layers of this framework.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Theme, components, tokens… everything will be introduced!","type":"text"}]}],"backgroundImage":"ic_unified_ds.png","action":{"overridingTitle":"Get started","isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get started"}]}},{"image":null,"kind":"volume","content":[],"chapters":[{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies"],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png","name":"Import of the Swift Package and choose its librairies","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will learn how to import the OUDS iOS Swift Package and which librairies it provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you should choose for your needs."}]}]},{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme"],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","name":"Preparation of the theme","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In this chapter you will see how to instanciate a theme and inject it inside your app","type":"text"}]}]},{"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-3-use-first-components"],"image":"ic_component_intro.png","name":"Use of first components provided by OUDS","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","